description:
Rob is a 25-year-old personal trainer from Texas. And he's all muscles and dick!

He's tall at 6'2" and totally ripped.

When asked about his relationship status, he said, "I have a girl that I mess around with."

"Do you ever mess around with guys?"

"Every now and then," he said with a smile. "I guess I'm bi-curious."

He kind of reminds me of Ethan!
title: Rob
